Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是奇怪的书看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被 诱导了吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他会这么说 真真儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这位住持 真的相信有灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好不容易来一趟寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就这样无功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像被什么可怕的东西紧紧地掐住了脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我这上不了台面的演技 还想跟此等老姜碰撞 是我失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不表露出我的本意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得让他相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有冲刺极限啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咻咻嘭嘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}{\fade(255,0,255,0,800,2200,3000)}这个是日本人模仿火车声音用的拟声词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H020210\bord0}合气道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子 在我的寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的寺院 搞什么飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想是成为一名科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过于忘我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上所有的事物都可以用科学来证明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让更多的人能够明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机到了我想告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚出去 你这个恶灵!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「人类随时都可能变成恶灵」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三星 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊 长野原前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才一阵子没见 你都上初中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为最近你都没来道场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近大学那边我也没去练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样你前阵子还得全日本第一了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魂淡天才型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在去道场?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 刚结束社团活动现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长野原来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那种练习多了反倒变得弱的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魂淡天才型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我承认她确实很强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不服气的是她从不好好练习还这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有着长野原前辈初一的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾取得代理师傅一本的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手可是那个代理师傅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在同为初中生的我却能力远不及她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团活动结束后就去道场练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末也不间断地练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像代理师傅所说的 金诚所至金石为开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 黑猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这个人 我的信心就开始动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想给她一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个情况的话 即使是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我现在只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天堂堂正正分出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天也能将代理师傅 将这个天才型的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代理师傅?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HCD84F1\3cHFFFFFF&}有关爱的两三事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(大福展销会)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 要好好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\c&H020204&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fn方正喵呜体\fad(300,300)\be7\an8\pos(101.887,641.25)}君\N临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸好像想让我接他的班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个气球 如果有小孩来了就给他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不干 得趁机逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气球…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充的二氧化碳啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}一言以概
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的最后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有个happy end
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\fn方正喵呜体\fad(300,300)\be7\bord1.125\c&HFDFDFC&\shad4.5\4c&H000006&\3c&HB3D4C4&\pos(187.925,855)}某\N圣\N诞\N节\N的\N一\N隅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士你想向圣诞老人许什么愿望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要巧克力点心 彩色铅笔 蛋糕橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 想要那么多真是太狡猾了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那么我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要两打鸡蛋 500克牛肉 还想要伊万·布宁的书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45\fade(255,0,255,0,800,3200,4000)}伊凡·布宁(Иван Алексеевич Вунин，1870－1953) 俄罗斯 19世纪末、 20世纪初一位继承了俄古典主义遗风的现实主义作家 布宁的创作生涯始于诗歌，创作成就主要是中短篇小说。1933年，获得诺贝尔文学奖。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是博士先许很多很多的愿望 所以名乃你只能许一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微多许一点点也没关系的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这个也让给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞士标准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey boy～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了! 是圣诞老人!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}(好吃的菠萝包)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\c&H020204&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fn方正喵呜体\fad(300,300)\be7\an8\pos(1804.528,420.75)}陷\N阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才陪他做着坑爹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧把这面罩脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼 好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想逃走么 刚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我在面具里加了点小机关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机关?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个面具里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涂了油漆!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨啦! 瞬间就把肉包子掉地上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还一口都没吃的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算啦算啦 微星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这个肉包子有毒的话 微星你可就会挂掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样反倒是赚到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赚到鬼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是放学后的最高乐事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要向前看的话 有失必有得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对掉落的肉包子抱以感谢之心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啥时候变成如此乐观之人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵 我决定了从今以后不管遇到什么都要向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 把没着地的部分拿起来不是还能吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对它的有毒设定抛到天际去了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样 把着地部分撕掉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～～～ 冰棒safe～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为向前看的精神而到来的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时向前看的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是肉包完全出局了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 这种时候更应该向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是肉包有毒的话 微星你就挂了呦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这变得也太快了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把下面那部分撕掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糊上冰棒的那部分总觉得各种无法接受…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 向前看向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs49.5}口癖“南无三” 原指“南无三宝”—佛、法、僧，也有“事情搞砸”、“完蛋了”的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南无三!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被刚才肉包子的热量融化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要想着如果冰棒有毒的话 这点小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都吃了好几口啦喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}(没中上)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 向前看效果连续挥棒落空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是上天给我的「要是吃两根就会坏肚子」的警告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 今天小菲你还真是持之以恒啊 不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这个冰棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有啊 如果不是冰棒而是雪糕的话就完全出局了诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是冰啊 去冲冲还能把灰冲掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对这点抱以感谢之心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这样了你还打算吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿了的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦小菲 积极点积极点～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜 人家不玩积极了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\fad(300,500)\be7\an8\pos(1766.038,306)\c&HFDFDFC&\shad1.125\4c&H000009&\3c&H332C2D&}向\N自\N由\N狂\N奔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还是不愿意做我的后继者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会设下第二甚至第三个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立花 你将来决定做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯… 我在犹豫到底是去上大学还是去专门学习料理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 料理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这这这这这…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了嫁给他!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡定点 立花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样绑住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去和阪本散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过一会儿朋友们要来开学习会 可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 博士我玩一会儿就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我出门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小鬼你在干嘛?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了 要勒死爷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我就听听你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人～ 哭泣着～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷现在想哭啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 鲨鱼是吧…小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你弄来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我解开啊魂淡!!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉会被咬也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪本 是狗狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被咬也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你…你怕什么死狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有绳子绑着的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能来咬你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话只能用三十六计的上策了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 闪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪本 闪不了了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不能放弃 放弃就完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去狗狗主人那里让她绑上绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死翘翘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 快点开动脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么方法吗×N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口袋里有个Gummi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63\fade(255,0,255,0,800,2200,3000)}Gummi是种果汁或其他味道的有弹性的糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个 趁它们吃着的时候赶紧闪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你做个可以逃生的道具出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 忘了那茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有制作道具的道具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魂淡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样了 要煮要烤随你便了啊你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要煮+要烤+随便你了=好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被吃掉了  要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被吃掉的话可能就会被吃的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶?博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭什么呀 迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子就是你上次说到的博士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪本也在一起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸 摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 佑子 赶紧把狗狗给干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子的毛软软的哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 赶紧把狗狗给干掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 被咬了所以想我帮你报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 等下有可能就要被咬了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你怕狗啊 你是Q太郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63\fade(255,0,255,0,800,2200,3000)}Q太郎是藤子·F·不二雄的妖怪Q太郎的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦 因为是狗狗所以会被咬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看 像这么老实的狗不会咬人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会咬人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会咬人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会咬人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要咬咬口香糖吗 冷个笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会·咬·啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你看着哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 给爪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ahh!!!!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑子没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}(抖抖抖抖抖)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不接近狗的话不会被咬的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑子被… 佑子被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 因为佑子是白痴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我们把佑子喊起来 一起去名乃家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识名乃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然认…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ahh!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了啊 不好好绑上绳子是不行的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和它们玩儿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊 差点被咬了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(医药日用杂货店 大工)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲨鱼巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅拿到了巧克力而且狗狗还走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 是吧阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是小鬼啊 居然害怕狗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说赶紧把我脖子上的绳子解下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为拿到了巧克力 所以就答应你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪本帮我解 太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷的小肉爪能解个喵啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让佑子帮解开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑子 帮我解~ 佑子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 佑子 佑子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂… 那个是……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇上好多狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了好多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 有巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力 巧克力 鲨鱼巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}巧克力 巧克力 鲨鱼巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 相生同学和长野原同学好慢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是往这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是闹哪样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪 小巴迪 你们到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和人之间是要互相帮助地生活的 隆志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对于动物之间也是一样的 隆志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能小看动物和人之间的羁绊哦 隆志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是清志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蜜瓜包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就永远地讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是要加蜜瓜的味道还是不要加蜜瓜的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的日常是第23话 敬请期待
